FBIS4-17356 "drsov079_b_94041" FBIS-SOV-94-079 Daily Report 22 Apr 1994 RUSSIAN NATIONAL AFFAIRS Political Issues Russia's Choice Appeals for May Day Measures Russia's Choice Appeals for May Day Measures LD2204164094 Moscow Mayak Radio Network in Russian 1400 GMT 22 Apr 94 LD2204164094 Moscow Mayak Radio Network Russian BFN [Text] The Russia's Choice faction in the State Duma today made public a statement containing an appeal to the bodies of executive power to ensure citizens' safety and constitutional order in Moscow. As is mentioned in the document, this has been prompted by the fact that, as the traditional spring celebrations approach, printed matter inciting people to violence is being distributed in factories and organizations.
